import Vue from 'vue'
import App from './App.vue'
import router from '@/router/index'
import TypeNav from '@/pages/home/TypeNav'

import {reqCategoryList} from '@/api/index'
Vue.component(TypeNav.name,TypeNav)

Vue.config.productionTip = false

reqCategoryList()

new Vue({
  render: h => h(App),
  router
}).$mount('#app')
